data.description: One of a kind country property on 7.58 acres of land in Hanford.This home is truly unique ,designed by Morro Bay architect George Nagano. Drive up the tree lined private driveway past one of two pastures. As you enter through the inviting entry way, you will step down into the living room that features ceiling to floor windows that give you a view of the mature shade trees, pool, and beautiful landscape. Cozy up in the built in couch next to the fireplace and enjoy all this beauty this room offers. The formal dining space has a built in bar that makes entertaining a breeze and is situated right off the Kitchen with large doors leading to the back patio and pool. The versatility that this home offers for year-round use is like no other. Three spacious guest bedrooms offer built in desks and shelving as well. There is an additional room that was used as an art studio with it's own private patio that can be used as a office, bedroom or craft area. The sprawling grounds offer two separate pastures, a small work shed and endless views. This home is a must see in person to appreciate the true beauty it holds! Owned Solar
